                "nuclide": "73-TA-181",
                "field_identifier": "ENR",
                "value": 0.998877
              },
              "free_text": [
                " High purity natural Ta",
                " (Ta-180 - 0.0123%, Ta-181 - 99.8877%) in metallic form",
                "was used as target materials for all irradiations. The",
                "stack of targets was composed of 32 marked tantalum",
                "foils (20 foils of 0.20 g/cm2+-1% and 12 foils",
                "of 0.148 g/cm2+-1% thick, and 16 mm in diameter). The",
                "thickness of each ta foil was determined by weight",
                "and area measurements."
              ]
            }
          ],
